{"questionId":"9739","questionHtml":"<p>Write down an expression for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"E\">\n  <mi>E</mi>\n</math></span> as a function of time.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"E = 5{\\left( {2\\,{\\text{sin}}\\,t} \\right)^2}\\,\\left( { = 20\\,{\\text{si}}{{\\text{n}}^2}\\,t} \\right)\">\n  <mi>E</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>5</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>sin</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n          <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>=</mo>\n      <mn>20</mn>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>si</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>n</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mi>t</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9739","referenceCode":"SPM.1.AHL.TZ0.7a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down an expression for E as a function of time.","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.9—Differentiating standard functions and derivative rules"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}